Then press the "a fabrics" to out side.

00:02:08.070 --> 00:02:28.730
Sew the front fabric and "b fabrics" with right side together.

00:02:29.200 --> 00:02:37.200
Then press the "b fabrics" to out side.

00:02:43.670 --> 00:03:07.200
Sew the front and back with right side together, leaving 10cm open for turning.

